1. follow the installation guide(http://doc.scrapy.org/en/1.0/intro/install.html) to install scrapy before running crawler

2. change your current working directory to the root dir of scrapy project

3. run the following command line to begin crawler
	scrapy crawl bestbuy -o bestbuy.csv
	
4. run the following python script "csv_converter.py" to adjust the format of the "bestbuy.csv"
	python csv_converter.py bestbuy.csv bestbuy_new.csv